# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:6
translate spanish emailwhitney_4ed503b7:

    # "I sit down in front of the laptop and open up the e-mail program."
    "Me siento frente al portátil y abro el programa de correo electrónico."

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:7
translate spanish emailwhitney_4885999e:

    # "The last email that Dad had received from her was the same day that I arrived back in town."
    "El último correo que papá recibió de ella fue el mismo día que volví a la ciudad."

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:8
translate spanish emailwhitney_3f762033:

    # "\"Where are you? Please reply.\""
    "«¿Dónde estás? Por favor, responde»."

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:9
translate spanish emailwhitney_db5b4c3c:

    # "And that is it. No more correspondence."
    "Y eso es todo. No hay más correspondencia."

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:10
translate spanish emailwhitney_957d73c5:

    # "I start writing."
    "Empiezo a escribir."

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:11
translate spanish emailwhitney_af04cae9:

    # "\"Whitney, my name is [pcname]. You have been talking to my dad for the last several months.\""
    "«Whitney, me llamo [pcname]. Has estado hablando con mi padre durante los últimos meses»."

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:12
translate spanish emailwhitney_0bc86332:

    # "\"He is now missing and I'm trying to find him.\""
    "«Ahora está desaparecido y estoy intentando encontrarlo»."

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:13
translate spanish emailwhitney_ce0bc1e0:

    # "\"I think that you know more about this than anybody else. Please contact me.\""
    "«Creo que sabes más sobre esto que nadie. Por favor, ponte en contacto conmigo»."

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:14
translate spanish emailwhitney_2761510b:

    # "\"I have not given your information to the police yet, but I will soon.\""
    "«Aún no he dado tu información a la policía, pero lo haré pronto»."

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:15
translate spanish emailwhitney_3dbffade:

    # "\"I just want to find my dad. Please help me.\""
    "«Solo quiero encontrar a mi padre. Por favor, ayúdame»."

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:16
translate spanish emailwhitney_e24f0fa4:

    # "At the bottom of the e-mail I include my phone number, then I press send."
    "Al final del correo incluyo mi número de teléfono y luego pulso enviar."

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:18
translate spanish emailwhitney_722c8b04:

    # "I hope she responds. She is by far my biggest lead on what happened to my dad."
    "Espero que responda. Ella es, con diferencia, mi mejor pista sobre lo que le pasó a mi padre."

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:19
translate spanish emailwhitney_aa64e5fa:

    # "If she doesn't reply, I wonder if Jez or Adrian could help me track her down - trace IP addresses or something?"
    "Si no responde, me pregunto si Jez o Adrian podrían ayudarme a localizarla: ¿rastrear direcciones IP o algo así?"

# game/Scenes/Other/emailwhitney.rpy:20
translate spanish emailwhitney_9c657a5a:

    # "For now, I'll give her a few days to get back to me."
    "Por ahora, le daré unos días para que me conteste."

